OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780927877
OL,3,CReading warehouse fined thousands for
OL,4,Crat infestation and food hygiene
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FContinued evidence of rat activity and
OL,8,Ffurther contaminated food were found,
OL,9,Fas well as 68 sheep heads near the
OL,10,Ffood, posing a potential public health
OL,11,Frisk.
OL,13,FThe premise was formally closed
OL,14,Ffollowing the council's inspection and
OL,15,Fall unsafe food was seized.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
