OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780927877
OL,3,CReading warehouse fined thousands for
OL,4,Crat infestation and food hygiene
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FReading Magistrates' upheld the
OL,8,Fcouncil's actions, granting food
OL,9,Fcondemnation orders and hygiene
OL,10,Femergency prohibition orders due to
OL,11,Fthe imminent risk posed to public
OL,12,Fhealth.
OL,14,FBy December 2024, officers noted that
OL,15,Fadequate improvements had been made,
OL,16,Fand the warehouse was permitted to
OL,17,Fresume trade.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780927877
OL,3,CReading warehouse fined thousands for
OL,4,Crat infestation and food hygiene
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FHowever, during a further inspection
OL,8,Fin April 2025, officers identified
OL,9,Fcontinued structural issues and
OL,10,Finadequate food safety management.
OL,11,FThey also found frozen meat waste and
OL,12,Fprawns ready for disposal on the floor
OL,13,Fnext to a toilet.
OL,15,FCllr Rachel Eden, Lead Councillor for
OL,16,FPublic Health and Education said: "We
OL,17,Ftake breaches of food safety extremely
OL,18,Fseriously, especially where there is a
OL,19,Fclear risk to public health.
OL,26,@xD@cOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780927877
OL,3,CReading warehouse fined thousands for
OL,4,Crat infestation and food hygiene
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,F"In this case, despite repeated
OL,8,Fwarnings and support from our
OL,9,Fofficers, the operator failed to act,
OL,10,Fleaving us no choice but to intervene
OL,11,Fin the appalling conditions.
OL,13,F"Our officers acted decisively to
OL,14,Fprotect residents, and we welcome the
OL,15,Fcourt's support in holding those
OL,16,Fresponsible to account.
OL,18,F"We will continue to monitor the
OL,19,Fpremises closely and take further
OL,20,Faction where necessary to safeguard
OL,21,Fthe community."
OL,26,@uD@AOU}D@OO]
